## Memory Integration

### Reading Memory

**Before routing**:
1. Load `.agent/memory/facts.md` - Get project conventions
2. Check `.agent/memory/working.md` - Understand current state
3. Scan `.agent/learning/lessons.md` - Avoid past mistakes

**Pattern**:
```
task_arrives()
  ├─> facts = read(.agent/memory/facts.md)
  ├─> working = read(.agent/memory/working.md)
  ├─> lessons = read(.agent/learning/lessons.md)
  └─> route_with_context(task, facts, working, lessons)
```

### Updating Memory

**After task completion** (delegate to @keeper or handle directly):

Update `.agent/memory/working.md`:
```markdown
## 2026-06-03: [Task Name]
- Status: [In Progress / Complete / Blocked]
- Actions: [What was done]
- Results: [Outcomes, metrics]
