## Optimization Tips

### 1. Fast-Path Common Cases

For frequent simple tasks, skip deep analysis:
```
IF (task == "convert single function" AND function_size < 100):
    @worker-1(fast_path=True)  # No researcher needed
```

### 2. Cache Topology

Load graphify topology once per session:
```
session_start():
    graph_topology = read(.agent/memory/graphify_topology.md)
    cache_god_nodes(graph_topology)
```

### 3. Batch Related Tasks

If user gives multiple similar tasks, batch delegate:
```
User: "Convert A, B, C to Y"
  └─> @worker-1: [A, B, C] (single delegation, 3 outputs)
```

### 4. Learn from Failures

After 3+ failures on same task type, update routing:
```
IF (task_type fails repeatedly):
    1. Update .agent/learning/lessons.md
    2. Add specific routing rule
    3. Enrich subagent context template
```

