## Maintenance

### Monthly Review

1. Check `.agent/learning/lessons.md` - Extract patterns
2. Review `.agent/memory/facts.md` - Update conventions
3. Re-run `/graphify .` - Update god node list
4. Test routing accuracy - Adjust rules if <95%

### When to Refactor

**Split a subagent** if:
- Context regularly exceeds 10K
- Handles >3 distinct task types
- Failure rate >10%

**Merge subagents** if:
- Delegation overhead dominates
- Tasks always sequential (never parallel)
- Responsibilities overlap >50%

